    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/a45ec450bedb6b6a5de7314dab58edf3.avif?t=1764754882\" width=700 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/e24bd8a32529183b65aa735a20ef48ff.avif?t=1764754882\" width=700 height=1786 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/0f3eabdf889c3c42c4e6a8d6f724fa4f.avif?t=1764754882\" width=700 height=696 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/4534490d77ce0a99de4cd2a5c21672ed.poster.avif?t=1764754882\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/4534490d77ce0a99de4cd2a5c21672ed.webm?t=1764754882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/4534490d77ce0a99de4cd2a5c21672ed.mp4?t=1764754882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-Paced Mech Action</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a rebel leader controlling a squad of three mechs, each with a different arsenal. Swap between mechs mid-combat and use their unique strengths tactically to overcome your foes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/2515582f85c4ffc207156a992c4108b2.poster.avif?t=1764754882\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/2515582f85c4ffc207156a992c4108b2.webm?t=1764754882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/2515582f85c4ffc207156a992c4108b2.mp4?t=1764754882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Boss Fights</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take down gargantuan mech bosses in a series of action-packed battles! Understand the enemy, execute evasive maneuvers, and exploit every weakness you find. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/f653093830dc3b227a567a5074e1ea36.poster.avif?t=1764754882\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/f653093830dc3b227a567a5074e1ea36.webm?t=1764754882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296470/extras/f653093830dc3b227a567a5074e1ea36.mp4?t=1764754882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Ultimate Fusion</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine your mechs through the power of Gattai! Together, you’re unstoppable. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*Assets may not be representative of the final product.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Trailer BGM Credit</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Gothamlicious&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kevin MacLeod </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i></p>",
